{
  "id": "5cb5e6c80c00b40017bb41d2",
  "title": "過程決定計画図",
  "created": 1555424969,
  "updated": 1555427036,
  "lines": [
    {
      "id": "5cb5e6c80c00b40017bb41d2",
      "text": "過程決定計画図",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1555424969,
      "updated": 1555424969
    },
    {
      "id": "5cb5e6caaff09e0000ede60a",
      "text": "[問題解決大全] P.210 で紹介されている",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1555424970,
      "updated": 1555425161
    },
    {
      "id": "5cb5e789aff09e0000ede60c",
      "text": "近藤次郎が『意思決定の方法――PDPCのすすめ』で提案した手法",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1555425161,
      "updated": 1555425177
    },
    {
      "id": "5cb5e799aff09e0000ede60d",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1555425177,
      "updated": 1555425177
    },
    {
      "id": "5cb5e799aff09e0000ede60e",
      "text": "\t[制約]を明らかにする",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1555425178,
      "updated": 1555426049
    },
    {
      "id": "5cb5e7a4aff09e0000ede60f",
      "text": "\tスタートを設定する：[現状]",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1555425188,
      "updated": 1555425199
    },
    {
      "id": "5cb5e7afaff09e0000ede610",
      "text": "\t到達すべきゴールを設定する：[理想]",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1555425200,
      "updated": 1555425211
    },
    {
      "id": "5cb5e7bcaff09e0000ede611",
      "text": "\tスタートとゴールをつなぐ",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1555425213,
      "updated": 1555425238
    },
    {
      "id": "5cb5e8d4aff09e0000ede618",
      "text": "\t\t使う記号",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1555425493,
      "updated": 1555425496
    },
    {
      "id": "5cb5e7d6aff09e0000ede612",
      "text": " \t\t□: 対策: [行動]",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1555425238,
      "updated": 1555425497
    },
    {
      "id": "5cb5e7f8aff09e0000ede613",
      "text": " \t\t○: 状態",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1555425272,
      "updated": 1555425497
    },
    {
      "id": "5cb5e802aff09e0000ede614",
      "text": " \t\t◇: 分岐点",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1555425282,
      "updated": 1555425497
    },
    {
      "id": "5cb5e84caff09e0000ede615",
      "text": " \t\tループが許容される",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1555425356,
      "updated": 1555425497
    },
    {
      "id": "5cb5e8b5aff09e0000ede617",
      "text": "\t\tまず最短経路でつなぐ",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1555425461,
      "updated": 1555425504
    },
    {
      "id": "5cb5e8e0aff09e0000ede619",
      "text": "\t\t\t最も楽観的なルート",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1555425505,
      "updated": 1555425514
    },
    {
      "id": "5cb5e8eaaff09e0000ede61a",
      "text": "\t\tありうる分岐点を考えて、書き足す",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1555425514,
      "updated": 1555425631
    },
    {
      "id": "5cb5e95faff09e0000ede61b",
      "text": "  だいたい書き終えたら以下を検討する",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1555425631,
      "updated": 1555425672
    },
    {
      "id": "5cb5e97eaff09e0000ede61c",
      "text": "  \t(a)矛盾はないか",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1555425663,
      "updated": 1555425665
    },
    {
      "id": "5cb5e981aff09e0000ede61d",
      "text": "  \t(b)抜けているものはないか",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1555425665,
      "updated": 1555425668
    },
    {
      "id": "5cb5e983aff09e0000ede61e",
      "text": "  \t(c)不測の事態への対策は十分か",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1555425668,
      "updated": 1555425668
    },
    {
      "id": "5cb5e6cbaff09e0000ede60b",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1555424971,
      "updated": 1555424971
    },
    {
      "id": "5cb5eabfaff09e0000ede625",
      "text": "備考",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1555425983,
      "updated": 1555426243
    },
    {
      "id": "5cb5e98caff09e0000ede61f",
      "text": " 事前に完全な「過程決定計画図」を作ることはできない",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1555425676,
      "updated": 1555425982
    },
    {
      "id": "5cb5e9adaff09e0000ede621",
      "text": " 時間が進むにつれて情報が増えるので、書き足していく",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1555425709,
      "updated": 1555425982
    },
    {
      "id": "5cb5e9f6aff09e0000ede622",
      "text": " 計画図通りに事態が進まなかった時は書き直す",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1555425782,
      "updated": 1555425982
    },
    {
      "id": "5cb5ea80aff09e0000ede623",
      "text": "\t情報不足でも作ることができる。事実の分析ではなく、作成者の問題認識の図解だから",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1555425920,
      "updated": 1555426036
    },
    {
      "id": "5cb5ead9aff09e0000ede626",
      "text": "\t新しい事実が明らかになって問題認識が更新された時には図も書き直される",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1555426010,
      "updated": 1555426026
    },
    {
      "id": "5cb5eaeaaff09e0000ede627",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1555426026,
      "updated": 1555426028
    },
    {
      "id": "5cb5eda4aff09e0000ede637",
      "text": "考察",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1555426724,
      "updated": 1555426725
    },
    {
      "id": "5cb5eb51aff09e0000ede629",
      "text": "「スタート」「ゴール」「対策」はそれぞれ「現実」「理想」「行動」と対応するだろうと[nishio.icon]が考えた",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1555426130,
      "updated": 1555426206
    },
    {
      "id": "5cb5eb54aff09e0000ede62a",
      "text": "\t「理想と現実のギャップを埋めるための行動を考える」というアプローチ",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1555426132,
      "updated": 1555426659
    },
    {
      "id": "5cb5ed62aff09e0000ede633",
      "text": "\t\tギャップが大きな時に単一の行動で埋めることができなくなる。",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1555426659,
      "updated": 1555426659
    },
    {
      "id": "5cb5ed0aaff09e0000ede62e",
      "text": "\tその場合に、より近い理想を立てるアプローチがある。",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1555426570,
      "updated": 1555426690
    },
    {
      "id": "5cb5ed83aff09e0000ede634",
      "text": "\t\t理想を近くすることで、ギャップを小さくする",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1555426691,
      "updated": 1555426702
    },
    {
      "id": "5cb5ed8eaff09e0000ede635",
      "text": "\t\tギャップが小さくなったのでそれを埋める行動も小さくなる",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1555426702,
      "updated": 1555426712
    },
    {
      "id": "5cb5ed97aff09e0000ede636",
      "text": "\t\tこのアプローチは、その行動の結果の次の行動を考えない",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1555426712,
      "updated": 1555426713
    },
    {
      "id": "5cb5ed4aaff09e0000ede631",
      "text": "\t\t将棋で例えるなら、相手の手を読まないことに相当する",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1555426634,
      "updated": 1555426647
    },
    {
      "id": "5cb5ed43aff09e0000ede630",
      "text": "\t過程決定計画図は、楽観的パスをまず最後まで通す",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1555426628,
      "updated": 1555426831
    },
    {
      "id": "5cb5ee04aff09e0000ede63b",
      "text": "\t\tその後、不確実性がある部分にできる範囲で枝分かれを足す",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1555426820,
      "updated": 1555426847
    },
    {
      "id": "5cb5ee1faff09e0000ede63c",
      "text": "\t\t将棋でいうなら相手がこちらの都合の良い手を打ってくれると想定している",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1555426847,
      "updated": 1555426877
    },
    {
      "id": "5cb5ee41aff09e0000ede63d",
      "text": "\t\t将棋の読みは、相手がこちらの一番都合の悪い手を打つ想定をする",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1555426882,
      "updated": 1555426902
    },
    {
      "id": "5cb5ee55aff09e0000ede63e",
      "text": "\t\t\t現実世界は必ずしもそうではない",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1555426902,
      "updated": 1555426913
    },
    {
      "id": "5cb5ee61aff09e0000ede63f",
      "text": "\t\t\t将棋と違って「起こりうること」の選択肢が無数にある",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1555426913,
      "updated": 1555426953
    },
    {
      "id": "5cb5ee89aff09e0000ede641",
      "text": "\t\t\t\t明日自分がトラックにはねられるかも知れない",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1555426953,
      "updated": 1555426990
    },
    {
      "id": "5cb5eeb7aff09e0000ede642",
      "text": "\t\t人間の認知能力にも限界があるから、まずは一番シンプルな「楽観的パス」から考えるのも理はある。",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1555427000,
      "updated": 1555427036
    },
    {
      "id": "5cb5edf5aff09e0000ede63a",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1555426805,
      "updated": 1555426991
    },
    {
      "id": "5cb5eda8aff09e0000ede639",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1555426728,
      "updated": 1555426728
    },
    {
      "id": "5cb5ea80aff09e0000ede624",
      "text": "[新QCの七つ道具]の1つ ",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1555425920,
      "updated": 1555425928
    }
  ]
}